{"type": "article", "id": 16234, "title": "不透水旅行包系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-19T06:00:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000425TxBCi2oh8SZDL6Ra.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t冲浪品牌 Finisterre 和德国防水设计品牌 Ortlieb 推出了这款旅行包，以求做到完全防水。采用一体成形的焊接方式，有效防止外面的气体进入，而 PVC-PU 材质，在减轻重量的同时，增加了耐用性。可以选择 20L 的单肩包或 40L 的双肩包两种容量，都有蓝色和黑色，<a href=\"http://www.finisterreuk.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=Ortlieb+\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143602VnoaScLybgqG18zm.jpg\" width=\"976\" height=\"510\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.52254098\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143602EBQX5b8w2Zs9JkoY.jpg\" width=\"575\" height=\"390\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67826087\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143602SOhLGg4YBjtiFlb7.jpg\" width=\"575\" height=\"390\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67826087\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261436037yAtYasHQ42b6vx1.jpg\" width=\"575\" height=\"390\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67826087\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143603KYgsaS78rI1QOtih.jpg\" width=\"575\" height=\"390\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67826087\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}